description: Dillan is back, and on his birthday no less! It was a day of firsts here at Sean Cody: Dillan taught Shaw how to surf, and Shaw taught Dillan how to eat ass…maybe he taught him too well; Shaw didn’t want our cute newbie to stop! “Where the fuck have you been?!” That didn’t matter. What mattered was that he was right there at that moment to pound him out! Dillan didn’t hesitate once, so he let his wild side roam free. By the end of it all, Shaw was covered in cum and Dillan had the best birthday yet!
title: Dillan & Shaw: Bareback
